data.description: BRAND NEW ROOF!! Searching for your dream home? We found it right here in Madisonville!! This better than new home is located on a large corner lot at the end of a quiet cul de sac. This Move-In-Ready house has so many upgrades including a fully screened in back porch, open floor plan, wood floors in living room, fireplace, computer nook off kitchen, granite counter tops, huge 2 car garage and MUCH MUCH More!! The backyard is fully fenced in, has a double gate for rear yard access, and comes complete with beautiful bamboo bushes for added privacy.  This incredible home is located in highly sought after Madisonville school district, High and Dry in Flood Zone C (the best), and within beautiful Raiford Oaks Subdivision. This subdivision features majestic live oaks, has park like green spaces, a community playground, and has a beautiful neighborhood pool for residents to enjoy. This home WONT last long so book your showing TODAY!!
